OL,3,CSheffield flats evacuated after
OL,4,Cbuilding partially collapses
OL,6,FSeveral flats on London Road in
OL,7,FSheffield have been evacuated after a
OL,8,Fbuilding partially collapsed overnight.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FLondon Road around 1am on Sunday 26
OL,12,FApril.
OL,14,FThe flats which are directly impacted
OL,15,Fsit above the Golden Stars takeaway
OL,16,Fand Modelanja tattoo shop.
OL,18,FSouth Yorkshire Fire and Rescue have
OL,19,Fconfirmed that no one has been hurt in
OL,20,Fthe incident.
